title: Bobbins, 1100–1400
medium: Medium: wood bobbins, cotton and wool yarns
description: Eleven small wooden bobbins painted at one end and bluntly pointed at the other end. Blue, brown, tan and red cotton and woolen yarns wound loosely around the group.
